{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595100/extras/about_the_game.gif?t=1735236261\" /><br><br>&quot;HeroBot!&quot; Is a 2d platformer inspired by Kirby and MegaMan. You play as HeroBot a robot that can grab and absorb your enemies and use their powers against them. You can also absorb two powers and mix them together for a stronger power. Absorb and mix powers to adapt to any situation!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595100/extras/HB_1.gif?t=1735236261\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595100/extras/mix_powers2.gif?t=1735236261\" /><br><br>Absorbing only one power at a time won't do in this adventure. Herobot is able to absorb two powers at once. The two powers will combine and become a greater power. Every power combination is its own power based on the two powers. Also, some of the best powers feature two of the same powers.   <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595100/extras/HB_3.gif?t=1735236261\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595100/extras/fight_crazy_bosses.gif?t=1735236261\" /><br><br>You will need to use your best skills and abilities in order to overcome the many powerful bosses in this game. Learning power combinations would definitely help picking the best power to combat the crazy bosses in the game. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595100/extras/HB_2.gif?t=1735236261\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595100/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735236261","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595100/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1735236